Plot:
With dreams of being an inventor, opportunist and eccentric elf Bernard D. Elf is made to
feel a fool yet again when his innovative creation to bring back people's favourite Christmas
memories back to life fails miserably. However he is then presented with the perfect opportunity
to prove his worth, when Santa is kidnapped by the evil Neville Baddington, and his demanding
mother Vera, who have their heart set on discovering Santa's big secret: how he delivers
presents across the world in just one night. However Bernard knows how he does it, using a
time travelling device to ensure all children wake up on Christmas morning with their
presents under the tree. The elf decides to use this to his advantage, as he plans on going
back in time and preventing the abduction from ever happening, and save Santa - and Christmas
- for the entire world.
